ue">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-solar-winds-secret-hammerheads-and-what-they-tell-us-about-heat-in-space</guid></item><item><title>发育中的免疫细胞如何微调其信号</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/how-developing-immune-cells-fine-tune-their-signals</link><description>VIB、根特大学和 VUB 的研究人员发现了两种对于免疫细胞发育至关重要的蛋白质如何在分子水平上协同工作。这些发现为介导从免疫威胁接收到的分子信号整合的关键机制提供了重要的见解。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-developing-immune-cells-fine-tune-their-signals.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 14:25:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/how-developing-immune-cells-fine-tune-their-signals</guid></item><item><title>电子是真实的吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/are-electrons-real</link><description>2023 年，哲学家 Philip Goff 在 X（以前称为 Twitter）上提出了一个看似简单的问题：“电子存在吗？”物理学家、哲学家和众多评论家纷纷做出回应。他们的反应从简短的驳斥到对科学知识本质的深刻反思。在这种热闹的背景下，三位学者对物理学家如何回答这个问题进行了正式调查。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/are-electrons-real.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 14:10:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/are-electrons-real</guid></item><item><title>贝壳模型的贝壳游戏</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-shell-models-shell-game</link><description>一项新实验解决了关于轻核中质子和中子能量的争议。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-shell-models-shell-game2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 13:55:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-shell-models-shell-game</guid></item><item><title>珊瑚研究可以通过解码纤毛驱动的流体流动来帮助解释不孕症和卵巢癌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/coral-study-could-help-explain-infertility-and-ovarian-cancer-by-decoding-cilia-driven-fluid-flows</link><description>曼彻斯特大学的研究人员与墨尔本大学和哥本哈根大学一起进行的一项研究可能是了解不孕症和卵巢癌等长期健康问题原因的关键。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/coral-study-could-help-explain-infertility-and-ovarian-cancer-by-decoding-cilia-driven-fluid-flows.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 13:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/coral-study-could-help-explain-infertility-and-ovarian-cancer-by-decoding-cilia-driven-fluid-flows</guid></item><item><title>聆听太阳的声音揭示了太阳周期之前隐藏的变化</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/listening-to-the-sun-reveals-previously-hidden-changes-to-solar-cycle</link><description>一项新的研究表明，在过去的四个太阳活动周期中，由于太阳“活跃的生物节律”引起的内部变化变得越来越“肤浅”。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/listening-to-the-sun-reveals-previously-hidden-changes-to-solar-cycle2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 13:25:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/listening-to-the-sun-reveals-previously-hidden-changes-to-solar-cycle</guid></item><item><title>罕见的观测揭示了 X9 太阳耀斑爆发前的情况</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/rare-observations-reveal-an-x9-solar-flare-before-it-erupts</link><description>太阳耀斑是来自太阳表面的强大辐射爆发，可能对地球电网造成严重破坏，损坏轨道卫星，并对宇航员造成严重的辐射风险。然而，尽管经过数十年的研究，引发这些火山喷发的过程仍然知之甚少。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/rare-observations-reveal-an-x9-solar-flare-before-it-erupts2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 13:10:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/rare-observations-reveal-an-x9-solar-flare-before-it-erupts</guid></item></channel></rss>